# Cloudflare Workers Static Assets redirects.
# Replaces the next.config redirects() that static export cannot emit.
# Evaluated before assets are served, so these fire even for existing pages.

# Host canonicalization. Each rule is host-scoped via an absolute source URL,
# so it is inert on the other domain (this file ships to both FR and EN builds).
# FR canonical host is www; EN canonical host is the apex (see .env.example).
https://mavilleideale.fr/* https://www.mavilleideale.fr/:splat 301
https://www.bestcitiesinfrance.com/* https://bestcitiesinfrance.com/:splat 301

/a-propos /about 301
